channel.title: One problem with moparscape server status
channel.description:
hey guys i need help every time i register a server it says
New server babzscape succesfully posted, however it will not show up on the list until it has been approved. Please allow at least 24 hours for the approval process. In order for it to be approved it must be online at the time it is checked again, if not online it will be deleted and you may post it again later. Click here to return to main page. Hit Counter
i have been waiting over 3 days help :confused: :confused:
admin would be nice if they helped out aswell
